Package: rPinecone
Type: Package
Title: Defines sub-lineages of a clonal expansion via an phylogenetic tree.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alexander Wailan
Maintainer: Alexander Wailan <aw19@sanger.ac.uk>
Description: The package will take a rooted ACCTRANS tree file and will define sub-lineages in a root-to-tip manner using a SNP  threshold and relatibility threhold.
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
Imports: geiger (>= 2.0.6), ape (>= 4.1), igraph (>= 1.1.2), BMhyd (>= 1.2-8), phangorn (>= 2.2.0), phytools (>= 0.6-20), RColorBrewer (>= 1.1-2)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
